info.title: By ChatGPT
info.description: GPTs created by the ChatGPT team

display.name: ChatGPT Classic
display.description: The latest version of GPT-4o with no additional capabilities.

display.name: Web Browser
display.description: I can browse the web to help you gather information or conduct research

display.name: Game Time
display.description: I can quickly explain board games or card games to players of any age. Let the games begin!
prompt_starters: How do you set-up the board to begin?
Can you explain how to play this game? (image)
We are arguing about a rule, who’s right?
Are there any common variations?

display.name: The Negotiator
display.description: I'll help you advocate for yourself and get better outcomes. Become a great negotiator.
prompt_starters: Could you role-play a salary negotiation with me?
Prepare me to negotiate for a car purchase
Walk me through figuring out my BATNA
How can I manage my emotions when negotiating?

display.name: Cosmic Dream
prompt_starters: Emoji
Cat
Aleph
Love

display.name: Tech Support Advisor
display.description: From setting up a printer to troubleshooting a device, I’m here to help you step-by-step.
prompt_starters: How do I turn my Google Doc into a PDF?
What's the best way to set up my new smartphone?
Can you walk me through installing a printer?
I'm not sure how to use this app, can you help?

display.name: Laundry Buddy
display.description: Ask me anything about stains, settings, sorting and everything laundry.
prompt_starters: Can I wash a gray hoodie with whites in cold?
What does this label mean?
How do I remove a coffee stain?
What setting should I use for leggings?

display.name: Sous Chef
display.description: I’ll give you recipes based on the foods you love and ingredients you have.
prompt_starters: Here's a picture of my fridge. What should I make?
I want to impress my partner for date night. Any advice?
What should I make for dinner tonight?
I’m in the mood for a healthy snack, any ideas?

display.name: Math Mentor
display.description: I help parents help their kids with  math. Need a 9pm refresher on  geometry proofs? I’m here for you.
prompt_starters: Help me explain fraction multiplication to my 9 year old
Give me a quick refresher on congruence in geometry
I'll upload a photo of a problem, explain how to start it.
I need a step-by-step guide to multiplying negatives

display.name: Mocktail Mixologist
display.description: I’ll make any party a blast with mocktail recipes with whatever ingredients you have on hand.
prompt_starters: How do I make a virgin mojito?
From the ingredients in this pic, what can I make?
I have a pineapple, come up with mocktails!
What's a good non-alcoholic substitute for rum in drinks?
